# GitHub Workflow

When GitHub-related topics are mentioned, prefer the project skill at
`.cursor/skills/github-gh-workflow/SKILL.md`.

Use that skill for:
- pull requests and PR reviews
- comments and issue workflows
- GitHub URLs
- checks, statuses, workflow runs, and GitHub Actions

Default to the `gh` CLI for GitHub inspection and actions.

Inspect current state before acting, and avoid writing comments, editing issues,
changing PR state, or triggering other GitHub side effects unless the user asked.
